    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Switch Poker is an online poker hand builder all about trading cards with your opponents!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283830/extras/1a1a6236e33a1ffdaa213dd7b55bfae5.poster.avif?t=1730484458\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283830/extras/1a1a6236e33a1ffdaa213dd7b55bfae5.webm?t=1730484458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283830/extras/1a1a6236e33a1ffdaa213dd7b55bfae5.mp4?t=1730484458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep strong cards for yourself and give away the rest to create the best hand possible.  <br>You'll need every edge you can get to win when playing against up to 8 other players.   <br>Think about what cards your opponent will trade with you to stay one step ahead!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283830/extras/0251ea79e66b570bf8d00f9b6307750a.poster.avif?t=1730484458\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283830/extras/0251ea79e66b570bf8d00f9b6307750a.webm?t=1730484458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283830/extras/0251ea79e66b570bf8d00f9b6307750a.mp4?t=1730484458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The definitive online poker trading experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-game chat - deceive your opponents by lying about what card you need, <br>or form short-term alliances to take down those in the lead.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer mode includes public and private lobbies, quick join, and join codes!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in Switch Poker's lounge-inspired world, complete with sleek, modern art.  <br>Let the jazzy soundtrack get you in a rhythm to  enjoy a thrilling poker trading session!</p>",
